    "body": "@Haroenv @francoischalifour @dhayab I meant have a single object argument, not keeping two arguments.\r\n\r\n```js\r\n({ items, results }) => items.map(fn).concat(results.nbHits)\r\n```\r\n\r\nWe use a similar pattern in Autocomplete's reshape for instance.",
